WEBVTT

00:01:26.503 --> 00:01:31.879
Je hivi ndivyo inavyokuwa kuwaza

00:01:31.903 --> 00:01:37.659
juu ya penzi ambalo halikuwahi kuwa hai
nje ya akili zangu au umbali?

00:01:37.683 --> 00:01:39.941
Kadiri ya muda, hakika nilipoteza upeo,

00:01:39.965 --> 00:01:42.291
nikidhani nilikosea
kuondoka pembeni yako.

00:01:42.315 --> 00:01:44.927
Lakini muda ni hakimu katili,

00:01:44.951 --> 00:01:47.018
hutufanya tudhani tulikuwa kwenye penzi.

00:01:47.042 --> 00:01:48.198
Na sasa

00:01:48.222 --> 00:01:49.742
Nimezeeka na majuto

00:01:49.766 --> 00:01:52.444
nikitamani ningekushikilia na kusahau tu.

00:01:52.468 --> 00:01:55.205
Ila siwezi nitakuwa tu nyumbani
huku nikitamani nyumbani,

00:01:55.229 --> 00:01:58.273
nikitamani ungekuwa wangu
na sikukuumiza kama nilivyofanya.

00:01:58.297 --> 00:02:00.730
Hatuwezi kurudi pale ambapo
tulikuwa na nafasi,